getRatingModelController

<T extends Rating,M extends ModifiableRating> RatingModelController<T,M> getRatingModelController(RatingModel<T> ratingModel)
                                                                                            throws CannotInstantiateControllerException
Returns a RatingModelController for the given model. The returned controller exposes a default locator only that allos to search by ObjectID or unique name only. No RatingModelLocator will be exposed.

Parameters:
ratingModel - The model
Returns:
a RatingModelController for the given model
